These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
House: modern, art-deco, futuristic, farmhouse, tower
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, surfing, baseball, badminton
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the tower house is on the right of the modern house##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
6. the modern house is in the middle##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| House   | art-deco | futuristic | modern | tower | farmhouse |
| Sport   | badminton    | tennis | surfing     | baseball       | weightlifting  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: spinach, banana, apricot, pomegranate, broccoli
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, iris, lily, marigold, sunflower
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person eating spinach is in the middle##1
5. the person eating banana is the person who growslily##1
6. the person who growssunflower is the person eating broccoli##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Food      | banana | apricot | spinach | pomegranate | broccoli |
| Flower   | lily  | marigold   | rose       | iris    | sunflower   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
House: cape-cod, tower, townhouse, farmhouse, colonial
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, march, january, december, may
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the tower house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| House        | townhouse | farmhouse | tower | cape-cod | colonial |
| Birthday   | march  | february      | may | january | december      |

