.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, spinach, strawberry, lettuce, corn
City: rome, venice, hannover, prague, liverpool
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food   | lettuce    | cabbage        | strawberry | spinach | corn |
| City     | rome | prague | liverpool  | venice   | hannover |

