.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  social-worker, firefighter, librarian, accountant, architect
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, ritmeester, pall-mall, bluemaster, aristoff
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the librarian##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is the architect##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is in the middle##1
5. the librarian is on the left of the social-worker##1
6. the aristoff-smoker is the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Job    | librarian   | social-worker     | firefighter   | accountant         | architect |
| Cigar   | swisher | bluemaster | pall-mall | aristoff | ritmeester     |

