.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, tea, lemonade, water
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, soul, metal, folk, funk
1. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of metal is the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Beverage       | lemonade   | tea   | almond-milk | water | cola |
| Music-Genre   | soul | metal | folk   | funk | hip-hop       |

