.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
City: prague, colone, paris, miami, edinburgh
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, oliveros, dannemann, pall-mall, bluemaster
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the swisher-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the dannemann-smoker is the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| City     | colone   | paris  | edinburgh      | prague | miami     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | dannemann | oliveros | swisher   | bluemaster |

