.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
There are 5 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, polish, turkish, malaysian
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, cat, lizard, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the malaysian##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the malaysian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
6. the canadian is on the right of the dutch##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Nationality     | dutch | canadian       | malaysian | turkish | polish    |
| Pet   | lizard   | rabbit | cat  | goldfish     | chinchilla |

