.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, train, car, roller, motorbike
There are 5 different favourite colors: amber, light-blue, emerald, yellow, lavender
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Transport         | roller | skateboard | car | motorbike | train |
| Color   | emerald       | yellow   | lavender         | light-blue   | amber   |

