3. the person who growsrose is the doctor##1
4. the architect is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
