3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the egyptian is on the far right##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
7. the person driving the tram is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Nationality   | canadian | colombian  | spanish | nigerian | egyptian |
| Transport    | bike    | motorbike | tram   | boat       | train        |

