.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
5 different games are played: chess, go, domino, bridge, poker
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, british, brazilian, colombian, spanish
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the british##1
2. the person playing bridge is the spanish##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing go is on the far right##1
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
6. the colombian is on the left of the person playing go##1
7. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Game    | chess | bridge          | domino    | poker | go  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | spanish | italian | colombian | british |

