.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, february, march, june, april
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, sprite, lemonade, milk
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Birthday   | march | october      | june | february | april |
| Beverage     | lemonade  | 7up | water     | milk     | sprite  |

