.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, reading, rock-climbing, filmmaking, camping
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: sports, disaster, family, animation, adventure
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Hobby      | camping | rock-climbing | gardening      | filmmaking | reading      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | animation       | sports | adventure  | family |

