.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
House: farmhouse, art-deco, townhouse, wooden, craftsman
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, sports, adventure, superhero, satire
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the wooden house is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the craftsman house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is the townhouse house##1
5. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the townhouse house##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| House           | wooden     | craftsman | farmhouse | townhouse  | art-deco |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | satire               | sports     | adventure | superhero |

