.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
House: ranch-style, futuristic, tower, townhouse, colonial
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, gardening, collecting, sudoku, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the townhouse house##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| House   | colonial     | tower       | ranch-style     | futuristic  | townhouse  |
| Hobby      | sudoku | hiking | gardening | dancing | collecting |

