.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, blues, pop, metal, disco
5 different games are played: poker, domino, whist, snooker, monopoly
1. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the person playing poker##1
4. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the fan of rock##1
6. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | disco | pop | rock | metal |
| Game           | monopoly | snooker  | domino    | poker  | whist   |

 